comments[7]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-06T16:47:17.517Z",codex-agent,Duplicate-check evidence used pm context pm search and open or in-progress lists. Net-new scope under pm-lwps for first-class update-many workflow with rollback semantics.
  "2026-04-06T17:08:53.092Z",codex-agent,"Progress: shipped new pm update-many command with filter selectors, deterministic dry-run item diff preview, checkpoint file creation, apply execution summaries, and --rollback restore workflow. Rollback uses captured target updated_at values per item to replay precise restores and emits per-item restored or failed rows."
  "2026-04-06T17:08:56.969Z",codex-agent,"Verification evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/update-command.spec.ts tests/unit/update-many-command.spec.ts tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts tests/unit/pi-agent-extension.spec.ts tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts passed (140 tests)."
  "2026-04-06T18:46:48.573Z",codex-agent,"Delivered native update-many flow: filter-targeted bulk updates, deterministic dry-run planning, checkpoint capture, rollback-by-checkpoint-id, and per-item row accounting. Wired main command surface/exports/contracts/tests, plus docs updates in README/PRD/ARCHITECTURE/CHANGELOG/AGENTS. Verification: pnpm build; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage."
  "2026-04-06T23:08:15.281Z",codex-agent,"Reopened as canonical remediation tracker under pm-o7be for current audit findings wave to avoid duplicate item creation. Scope retained from prior implementation lineage and expanded for new report deltas only. Decision rationale: duplicate-check sweep in this run found no open/in-progress item directly covering this exact delta while this closed item already contains closest historical context, linked artifacts, and verification lineage."
  "2026-04-07T00:02:39.757Z",codex-agent,"In-progress implementation: expanded update-many mutation surface to parity with update for linked arrays (dep/comment/note/learning/file/test/doc/reminder/event plus clear/replace controls), added planning support that marks linked-array operations actionable in dry-run/apply, and aligned command contracts/completion/help surfaces. Verification so far: pnpm vitest tests/unit/update-many-command.spec.ts tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts (92 passed), pnpm build, and pnpm vitest tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts (28 passed)."
  "2026-04-07T00:11:33.784Z",codex-agent,"Completion evidence: update-many now accepts linked-array repeatables and clear/replace controls with deterministic dry-run/apply planning parity. Verified with pnpm build, node scripts/run-tests.mjs test (1002 passed), node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (1002 passed, 100% thresholds), and targeted release-readiness checks for update-many help/flags."
